WHY DO WE COLLECT YOUR DATA ?
To Operate the Services
Purpose: To run the services effectively, including payment verification.
Legal Basis: Necessary to fulfill our contract with you.
Data Collected: Identification data, contact information, usage data.
Retention Period: Stored during service usage and up to 3 years after last contact.
To Improve Player Experience
Purpose: To develop and enhance the services and support.
Legal Basis: Our legitimate interest in providing a great user experience.
Data Collected: Identification data, contact information, technical data, usage data, geolocation (country level).
Retention Period: Up to 2 years after last contact.
To Show Personalized Ads
Purpose: To deliver targeted advertising based on your behavior and preferences.
Legal Basis: Your consent.
Data Collected: Identification data, contact information, connection data, technical data, any correspondence.
Retention Period: Up to 2 years after last contact or until you withdraw consent.
To Maintain Service Integrity
Purpose: To monitor and prevent fraud and ensure fair use.
Legal Basis: Our legitimate interest in preventing fraud and ensuring a safe environment.
Data Collected: Identification data, any relevant correspondence.
Retention Period: Up to 3 years after last contact.
WITH WHOM DO WE SHARE YOUR DATA ?
Only aggregated, anonymized data is periodically transmitted to external services to aid the Service Provider in the objectives detailed above. The Service Provider may share your information with third parties in the ways that are described in this privacy statement. Below are the links to the Privacy Policy of the third-party service providers used by the Services:
